'''Fax Ventures''' was a company founded by [[Alara Fax]], a former criminal who used her illegal earnings to fund the company at first. Fax Ventures held many investments and operations throughout the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]], including a [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operation that mined [[Aluminite]] and [[Corax]] Ore from the [[Kadal Asteroid Field]] and processed it on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bestal Three]]. Bestal Three was also the location of their most impressive operation, where they used the crusty seeds from [[Vortal tree|Vortal Trees]] for medicinal purposes, creating [[Medpac/Legends|medpacs]] which were roughly 25% more effective than their regular counterparts.

